---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Sobre Nosotros | Maserati";

// Datos para la línea de tiempo o valores
const values = [
    {
        title: "Innovación Audaz",
        desc: "Desde 1914, desafiamos lo ordinario. No seguimos tendencias, las creamos.",
        icon: "/assets/images/sobreNosotros/inspiration.svg" // Rayo
    },
    {
        title: "Estilo Italiano",
        desc: "La elegancia no es una opción, es nuestra esencia. Diseño atemporal en cada curva.",
        icon: "/assets/images/sobreNosotros/italiaIcon.svg" // Imagen/Arte
    },
    {
        title: "Pasión por el Motor",
        desc: "El sonido de un Maserati no es ruido, es música. Una sinfonía de potencia.",
        icon: "/assets/images/sobreNosotros/motoreMaserati.png" // Reloj/Tiempo/Motor
    }
];
---

<Layout title={title}>
    
    <div class="relative pt-32 pb-20 px-6 text-center z-10 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full z-0 opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
            <img src="/assets/images/logos-image/logoMaserati.png" class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-[600px] opacity-10 blur-sm rotate-12" />
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-maserati-blanco mb-6 tracking-tight relative z-10">
            Más de un Siglo de <span class="text-maserati-amber">Excelencia</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-maserati-plata max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl relative z-10">
            Maserati es una historia de familia, de desafíos y de victorias. Desde un pequeño taller en Bolonia hasta convertirse en un icono mundial del lujo.
        </p>
    </div>

    <section class="bg-maserati-negro py-20 px-6 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-32">
            
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 md:gap-20">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative group">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-maserati-azul/20 transform translate-x-4 translate-y-4 rounded-lg transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-2 group-hover:translate-y-2"></div>
                    <img 
                        src="/assets/images/sobreNosotros/hermanosMaserati.jpg" 
                        alt="Hermanos Maserati" 
                        class="relative rounded-lg shadow-2xl w-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                    <span class="text-maserati-amber font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-2 block">1914 - Bolonia</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">El Comienzo de una Leyenda</h2>
                    <p class="text-maserati-plata leading-relaxed mb-6 text-lg">
                        Todo comenzó en un pequeño garaje en via de’ Pepoli, Bolonia. Alfieri, Ettore y Ernesto Maserati compartían una única obsesión: la velocidad.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-maserati-plata leading-relaxed">
                        No solo querían construir coches; querían dominar la pista. Su visión combinaba la ingeniería mecánica pura con una estética que definiría el "Gran Turismo" italiano para siempre.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12 md:gap-20">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative group">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-maserati-azul/20 transform -translate-x-4 translate-y-4 rounded-lg transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-2 group-hover:translate-y-2"></div>
                    <img 
                        src="/assets/images/sobreNosotros/estatuaNeptuno.webp" 
                        alt="Estatua de Neptuno" 
                        class="relative rounded-lg shadow-2xl w-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 text-left md:text-right">
                    <span class="text-maserati-amber font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-2 block">El Símbolo</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">El Tridente de Neptuno</h2>
                    <p class="text-maserati-plata leading-relaxed mb-6 text-lg">
                        Fue Mario Maserati, el único hermano artista, quien creó el logo. Inspirado en la estatua de Neptuno de la Piazza Maggiore de Bolonia, eligió el Tridente.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-maserati-plata leading-relaxed">
                        Un símbolo de fuerza y vigor apropiado para un coche deportivo. Los colores rojo y azul fueron tomados del estandarte de la ciudad de Bolonia.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-maserati-negro py-24 px-6 border-t border-maserati-gris/20 relative">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-16 uppercase tracking-widest">Nuestro <span class="text-maserati-amber">ADN</span></h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
                {values.map((item) => (
                    <div class="bg-maserati-gris/30 p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/5 hover:border-maserati-amber/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 group">
                        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-maserati-negro rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 border border-maserati-azul/30 group-hover:border-maserati-azul group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(31,64,104,0.5)] transition-all">
                            <img 
                                src={item.icon} 
                                alt={item.title} 
                                class="w-8 h-8 object-cover opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" 
                                width="50"
                                height="50"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">{item.title}</h3>
                        <p class="text-maserati-plata text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            {item.desc}
                        </p>
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative h-screen min-h-[600px] flex flex-col items-center justify-start pt-32 md:justify-center md:pt-0 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <img 
                src="/assets/images/sobreNosotros/granturismo-folgore-grey-front-side-view-mobile.webp" 
                alt="Maserati Folgore Mobile" 
                class="block md:hidden w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
            
            <img 
                src="/assets/images/sobreNosotros/granturismo-folgore-grey-side-view-on-the-road-night-desktop.webp" 
                alt="Maserati Folgore Desktop" 
                class="hidden md:block w-full h-full object-cover"
            />

            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-48 bg-linear-to-b from-maserati-negro to-transparent z-10"></div>

            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-48 bg-linear-to-t from-maserati-negro to-transparent z-10"></div>
            
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-maserati-negro/30 z-0"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col items-center">
            
            <span class="text-maserati-amber font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-4 md:mb-6 animate-pulse">
                El Futuro es Eléctrico
            </span>
            
            <img 
                src="/assets/images/sobreNosotros/folgore-logo-white.webp" 
                alt="Logo Folgore" 
                class="w-56 md:w-96 h-auto mb-6 md:mb-8 drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,255,255,0.3)]"
            />
            
            <p class="text-white/90 text-base md:text-xl mb-8 md:mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl text-shadow-sm">
                La nueva era de Maserati. 100% eléctrico.<br class="md:hidden"> 
                El rugido cambia, la pasión permanece.
            </p>

            <a href="/merch" class="group relative overflow-hidden inline-block border border-white/40 text-white px-8 py-3 md:px-10 md:py-4 rounded-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-xs md:text-sm font-bold hover:border-white transition-all duration-300 bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm">
                <span class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-white/10 transform -translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-transform duration-300"></span>
                <span class="relative">Descubrir Gama</span>
            </a>

        </div>
    </section>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-maserati-negro py-24 px-6 border-t border-maserati-gris/10">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 md:gap-16">
                
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
                    
                    <div class="relative group mb-6">
                        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-linear-to-tr from-maserati-amber to-maserati-gris rounded-full opacity-60 blur group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-1000"></div>
                        <img 
                            src="/assets/images/sobreNosotros/Maurizio-Zuares.jpg" 
                            alt="Mauricio Zuares" 
                            class="relative w-56 h-56 object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-maserati-negro shadow-2xl"
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/maurizio-zuares-979071b6" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-maserati-gris text-white hover:bg-[#0077b5] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-white/5">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
                        </a>
                        
                        <a href="https://x.com/Maserati_HQ" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-maserati-gris text-white hover:bg-black hover:border-white hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-white/5">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
                        </a>

                        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/maserati/" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-maserati-gris text-white hover:bg-linear-to-tr hover:from-yellow-400 hover:via-red-500 hover:to-purple-500 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-white/5">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1112.63 8 4 4 0 0116 11.37zm1.5-4.87h.01M7.5 3h9a4.5 4.5 0 014.5 4.5v9a4.5 4.5 0 01-4.5 4.5h-9A4.5 4.5 0 013 16.5v-9A4.5 4.5 0 017.5 3z"></path></svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Mauricio Zuares</h2>
                    <p class="text-maserati-amber font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-8">Presidente</p>
                    
                    <div class="relative">
                        <svg class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-12 h-12 text-maserati-plata opacity-10 transform -scale-x-100" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21L14.017 18C14.017 16.8954 14.9124 16 16.017 16H19.017C19.5693 16 20.017 15.5523 20.017 15V9C20.017 8.44772 19.5693 8 19.017 8H15.017C14.4647 8 14.017 8.44772 14.017 9V11C14.017 11.5523 13.5693 12 13.017 12H12.017V5H22.017V15C22.017 18.3137 19.3307 21 16.017 21H14.017ZM5.0166 21L5.0166 18C5.0166 16.8954 5.91203 16 7.0166 16H10.0166C10.5689 16 11.0166 15.5523 11.0166 15V9C11.0166 8.44772 10.5689 8 10.0166 8H6.0166C5.46432 8 5.0166 8.44772 5.0166 9V11C5.0166 11.5523 4.56889 12 4.0166 12H3.0166V5H13.0166V15C13.0166 18.3137 10.3303 21 7.0166 21H5.0166Z"></path></svg>
                        
                        <blockquote class="text-maserati-plata text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed italic z-10 relative">
                            "Maserati no es solo una marca de automóviles, es una celebración de la excelencia italiana. Nuestro compromiso es mantener viva la llama de la pasión mientras conducimos hacia un futuro sostenible y emocionante."
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>